{"tid":134541,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"第一次睇完breaking bad，唔明個結局","createTime":"2017-02-25T14:25:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-26T07:37:48.000Z","uid":3560,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7ecc5647f3a7235db7303e6b4ed2e4a8448df9ba","tid":134541,"uid":3560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T14:25:56.000Z","msg":"最尾嗰幾集，Walt逃走去New Hampshire之後<br />\n幫佢走佬條友話佢係The most wanted man in the nation。<br />\n但其實從來都無足夠証據指証佢。<br />\n<br />\n首先，Hank係由見到Gale本書開始查Walt<br />\n到最後team up Jesse同Steve Gomez<br />\n但都無乜「實質」証據去拉Walt<br />\n所以先要引佢去沙漠道挖錢<br />\n而喺挖到錢之前，Hank同Steve已經死左<br />\n但亦都無証據係Walt殺（實際上亦都唔係）<br />\n而淨係得Marie知Hank去左捉Walt無返到黎<br />\n<br />\n咁即係，其實由始至終<br />\n係得Marie（或者同Skyler）一面之詞去指証Walt<br />\n就算Walt自首，都好大機會告唔入或者打得甩<br />\n<br />\n所以我唔明點解電視會咁高調講Heisenberg case<br />\n仲要訪問埋Gretchen同Elliot<br />\n哩下好CCTVB<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實只要Walt一直否認Marie講嘅野<br />\n同Jr講Marie講大話<br />\n可能連佬都唔洗走"},{"pid":"bc42d9649acfa2a9ac11d2d2354f062d78be4419","tid":134541,"uid":3560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T14:26:28.000Z","msg":"對唔住，好長<br />\n但真係好震撼"},{"pid":"394d577d8f172bda627e1efcd8c94aa057669aa1","tid":134541,"uid":3560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T14:29:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 求解答"},{"pid":"b5a9575b7890598fcf38640dc7a9d7482abdbf2c","tid":134541,"uid":3560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T14:50:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2377b39d58ac02f3a6ea0682e302f241c374cd66","tid":134541,"uid":8129,"like